Package cp213

Class CountedItem<T extends Comparable<T>>

java.lang.Object
cp213.CountedItem<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<CountedItem<T>>
public class CountedItem<T extends Comparable<T>> extends Object implements Comparable<CountedItem<T>>
Stores a item and an occurrence count for that item. The item must be Comparable so that it can be compared and sorted against other values of the same type.

2023-09-06

      public int compareTo(CountedItem<T> target)
